  <description type="morphology">Stems 1–3(–3.7) dm, densely hirsute proximally, glabrous distally. Cauline leaves:
        blade flat distally, margins dentate, surfaces hirsute. Racemes secund; rachis straight.
        Fruiting pedicels 2–5 mm, sparsely pubescent or glabrous. Flowers: sepals rose to lavender
        or purple, 5–7 mm, glabrous or sparsely pubescent; petals purple, 8–11 mm; adaxial filaments
        6–8 mm. Fruits divaricate to ascending, curved upward; valves glabrous or sparsely
        pubescent. 2n = 28.</description>
